{"tid":1504794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[強烈建議]無衝的目標 就全部放棄陣地戰 轉 遊擊","createTime":"2019-08-25T11:42:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T15:21:01.000Z","uid":94771,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"91cacf631d817bee87ccfa305789e656e0a08014","tid":1504794,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:42:30.000Z","msg":"根本陣地戰要打就一定要有目標 例如612<br />\n無目標個D陣地你根本唔會有動力推前<br />\n<br />\n每次有地區遊行 就唔該出返去無封鐵的地帶 <br />\n<br />\n先開始去唔同地方打遊擊 <br />\n<br />\n最理想就封完路好走 封佐路popo都要開返條路出來 一樣可以消耗到佢地<br />\n<br />\n係心態無準備同有目標個時 唔好再有同popo的對峙戰 損耗太大又無咩實質大的成果<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b9693301d5184a32b323a98a297837775c62fe","tid":1504794,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:43:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00f34e3ec9d2bfbb4fdf9074855ab04b4050983","tid":1504794,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:59:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea17f99eb74eff9c61efa6176bcda8ecb01fea8","tid":1504794,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc78e44480909d966a6cd162fcc4aef8b728275e","tid":1504794,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78aeb534dd47d77ddab8146b5808e7a1fa19d909","tid":1504794,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f045e2d658a8cf47785b466d9411aadcfe8e6c7","tid":1504794,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s